-- helper to compute actual speed value
local function actualSpeed()

end

-- Movement loop (per-frame, stoppable, resumable)
local function moveLoop()
	-- if index passed end, reset to 1 so Start always does something
	if currentIndex > #waypoints then currentIndex = 1 end

	while isRunning and currentIndex <= #waypoints do
		local targetCFrame = waypoints[currentIndex]
		if not targetCFrame or not hrp then break end

		local targetPos = targetCFrame.Position
		local threshold = 1.5

		-- move per-frame toward target
		while isRunning and hrp and (hrp.Position - targetPos).Magnitude > threshold do
			local dt = RunService.Heartbeat:Wait()
			-- recalc direction each frame (in case player bumped)
			local dir = (targetPos - hrp.Position)
			local dist = dir.Magnitude
			if dist <= 0.0001 then break end
			local dirUnit = dir.Unit

			-- step this frame
			local step = actualSpeed() * dt
			if step > dist then step = dist end

			local newPos = hrp.Position + dirUnit * step
			-- set CFrame facing movement direction
			hrp.CFrame = CFrame.new(newPos, newPos + dirUnit)
		end

		-- if stopped by user, break keeping currentIndex (resume)
		if not isRunning then break end

		-- reached target -> advance index
		currentIndex = currentIndex + 1
	end

	-- finished all waypoints or stopped
	if isRunning and currentIndex > #waypoints then
		-- finished full route: stop and reset index if you want; here we stop and reset
		isRunning = false
		currentIndex = 1
		startBtn.Text = "▶️ Start"
		startBtn.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0,200,0)
		if runTrack then pcall(function() runTrack:Stop() end) end
	end
end
